works.description: Dear Google, you had helped me in the past and need your help again. When we do a google image search for "spinner ring gears" we seen that a chinese website took my image from my home page. The blue background with image of my ring.  As a result, please remove this from Image search. Prior notes will show/prove that i am the rightful owner since I have had to file other reports. Thank you for your help and email if needed.
